org.intermine.bio.ontology

Class OboTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.bio.ontology.OboTerm

  • public class OboTerm
extends java.lang.Object
    Extension of DagTerm that adds a namespace attribute that is specific to the OBO format.
